    curvature <m>\kappa=1/r</m>.
  </p>
</statement>
</exercise>

<p>
As we said earlier, the curvature of a general curve need not be
constant, but we can still apply <xref ref="EQUATIONCurvatureDef2">formula</xref>.
</p>
